WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 15]

03:00.690 --> 03:01.720
Master.

03:01.740 --> 03:03.140
Long time no see.

03:03.170 --> 03:04.820
How are you?

03:05.510 --> 03:07.280
I left Ning'an City

03:07.300 --> 03:09.220
and am now back in Ning'an City.

03:09.290 --> 03:11.010
Many things happened along the way

03:11.040 --> 03:12.040
and I learned a lot.

03:12.760 --> 03:14.150
I had a few near-death experiences.

03:14.220 --> 03:16.660
Fortunately, Fan Yue has been protecting me

03:16.690 --> 03:18.410
so I'm safe.

03:18.710 --> 03:19.800
But I only know now that

03:19.800 --> 03:22.170
Fan Yue has Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal in him.

03:22.610 --> 03:23.310
[Spirit Pill]

03:22.880 --> 03:25.090
I absorbed the second Contemplation in the Outlanders' City.

03:25.240 --> 03:27.870
He lost another star to protect me

03:27.870 --> 03:29.760
and suffered the pain of his soul burning.

03:29.790 --> 03:31.760
There are only two stars left now.

03:31.790 --> 03:34.030
Master, do you have a solution?

03:36.630 --> 03:39.000
I've tried all the common elixirs

03:39.020 --> 03:40.410
but they didn't work.

03:40.660 --> 03:41.940
You once said

03:41.970 --> 03:43.690
there was a first-grade elixir in the world.

03:43.710 --> 03:46.650
It can even withstand the thunder tribulation of a high-up Eternal ascending.

03:46.670 --> 03:48.390
If I can make it,

03:48.420 --> 03:50.110
will it help Fan Yue

03:50.190 --> 03:52.190
suppress the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal?

04:07.150 --> 04:08.780
Why is my nose bleeding again?

04:10.010 --> 04:12.500
Seems like I should drink more herbal tea.

04:29.320 --> 04:30.310
I'll refine it.

04:38.230 --> 04:38.880
It hurts.

04:38.900 --> 04:39.680
Stop!

04:39.680 --> 04:40.650
Stop beating me!

04:40.680 --> 04:42.409
It hurts.

04:58.990 --> 05:02.330
♫The person standing far away♫

05:03.340 --> 05:05.260
♫Don't be afraid♫

05:06.050 --> 05:10.420
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

05:11.610 --> 05:17.850
♫Walk towards me♫

05:19.930 --> 05:22.510
♫My heart feels so...♫

05:23.120 --> 05:25.940
♫Moved♫

05:23.720 --> 05:24.630
Mu.

05:36.960 --> 05:38.400
Fan Yue.

05:40.430 --> 05:43.190
Mu is also you.

05:53.010 --> 05:54.010
Mu?

05:55.980 --> 05:57.890
I usually call you Mu

05:57.920 --> 05:59.490
because you have "Mu" in your written name.

05:59.520 --> 06:00.790
But you are the Demon King of the Polar Realm.

06:00.810 --> 06:01.860
So I can't call you

06:01.890 --> 06:03.620
by that name in front of others.

06:07.340 --> 06:08.390
What a nonsense! One says it like it's real,

06:08.390 --> 06:09.510
and the other dares to believe it.

06:11.000 --> 06:12.000
But for now,

06:13.060 --> 06:14.620
let's say our goodbyes.

06:27.340 --> 06:28.270
One dares to kiss,

06:28.270 --> 06:29.800
and the other didn’t hide.

06:30.170 --> 06:31.390
He took on my looks

06:31.390 --> 06:32.750
and used me as an excuse–

06:32.780 --> 06:34.420
the things he did are absolutely ridiculous!

06:41.940 --> 06:42.980
Today's medicine.

06:43.480 --> 06:44.190
Leave it.

06:47.320 --> 06:48.740
Remember to eat it.

06:49.230 --> 06:50.560
You're leaving?

06:53.020 --> 06:54.730
Didn't you ask me to leave it?

06:54.760 --> 06:56.560
And that's all you're going to do?

06:56.680 --> 06:58.570
Aren't you going to say anything more?

06:58.590 --> 06:59.909
Am I supposed to?

06:59.940 --> 07:01.700
You were more patient when you

07:01.720 --> 07:02.950
took care of Mu in Outlanders' City.

07:04.200 --> 07:05.490
Mu lost his memory.

07:05.510 --> 07:06.490
He knows nothing.

07:06.520 --> 07:08.350
Of course I have to teach him everything little by little.

07:08.370 --> 07:09.770
He knows nothing?

07:10.180 --> 07:12.340
He knows nothing but kissing people, right?

07:14.920 --> 07:16.240
That was a farewell.

07:16.270 --> 07:17.800
You're defending him now?

07:18.530 --> 07:19.580
Defending him

07:19.700 --> 07:21.120
is defending you.

07:25.120 --> 07:26.040
See?

07:26.680 --> 07:28.700
You know how to dodge when someone approaches you.

07:29.200 --> 07:30.880
What are you trying to say?

07:30.900 --> 07:32.250
What I'm trying to say is...

07:35.080 --> 07:39.390
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

07:42.780 --> 07:46.200
♫You are my distant call♫

07:46.760 --> 07:51.180
♫You are my first and last♫

07:51.990 --> 07:57.890
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

07:58.280 --> 08:01.360
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

08:01.770 --> 08:05.980
♫Let's never let go♫

08:05.650 --> 08:07.250
That’s what you can’t avoid.

08:08.240 --> 08:09.690
This is my kiss.

08:12.550 --> 08:13.510
Why...

08:13.860 --> 08:15.450
I just want to tell you

08:16.180 --> 08:17.510
that Mu and I

08:17.540 --> 08:18.690
are different.

08:19.210 --> 08:21.120
Why do you want to prove that you are different so much?

08:21.150 --> 08:22.270
No reason.

08:22.790 --> 08:24.400
I just don’t like that fool.

08:24.420 --> 08:25.940
Mu is not a fool.

08:26.870 --> 08:28.350
He is the old you,

08:28.520 --> 08:29.720
the original Fan Yue.

08:31.060 --> 08:33.470
I've never seen you as two different people.

09:15.270 --> 09:16.380
Master.

09:18.280 --> 09:19.410
I'm incompetent,

09:19.570 --> 09:22.090
having to ask you to take the risk to come to this dangerous place.

09:22.120 --> 09:24.290
The Cold Spring Palace is heavily guarded.

09:24.310 --> 09:25.840
If anything happens to Master,

09:25.870 --> 09:27.310
even death is a light punishment for me.

09:30.240 --> 09:31.900
You are in danger.

09:31.990 --> 09:34.390
How can I stand by and watch?

09:35.110 --> 09:36.800
You've suffered.

09:38.600 --> 09:40.260
Take this pill.

09:40.360 --> 09:42.310
It can protect your heart and meridians.

09:48.440 --> 09:49.810
Fu Ling

09:50.010 --> 09:51.020
saved you?

09:51.090 --> 09:51.850
Yes.

09:52.370 --> 09:54.130
Fu Ling used her demonic flower armor

09:54.150 --> 09:55.980
to protect me from the attack.

09:56.040 --> 09:57.370
But don't worry, Master.

09:57.600 --> 09:59.080
I've killed the demonic flower

09:59.240 --> 10:00.640
and am a puppet of a demoness no more.

10:00.820 --> 10:02.690
60,000 years ago, the Hidden Lord cause turmoil in the world

10:02.710 --> 10:03.800
and the Divine Race perished.

10:03.830 --> 10:05.710
There is no more gods in the world.

10:06.250 --> 10:07.800
But Zhen Yu took the risk

10:07.830 --> 10:10.520
of having the Eternals and demons join hands

10:10.540 --> 10:12.620
and proposed the God-making Formation.

10:12.950 --> 10:15.520
This formation seems to be a trap,

10:15.750 --> 10:18.450
but it has all kinds of deception.

10:18.990 --> 10:20.440
If it's not traceable,

10:20.480 --> 10:22.360
the King of Outlanders wouldn't believe it easily.

10:22.380 --> 10:25.150
Besides, does Zhen Yu's motive of using the divine sword

10:25.170 --> 10:27.680
to retrieve the divine stone have something to do with God-making?

10:27.710 --> 10:29.040
This remains

10:29.060 --> 10:30.160
unknown to us.

10:31.170 --> 10:33.430
If he succeeds in God-making,

10:34.410 --> 10:36.730
everyone will be in danger.

10:36.760 --> 10:38.440
Why don’t you

10:38.470 --> 10:40.750
gather everyone to attack the Cold Spring?

10:41.620 --> 10:43.140
I can't do that.

10:45.250 --> 10:49.570
We don't know Cold Spring's army size and actual plans.

10:49.880 --> 10:50.910
Other than Fu Ling,

10:50.910 --> 10:52.240
there's another Demon Lord

10:52.260 --> 10:55.570
named Chen Ye under Zhen Yu.

10:55.610 --> 10:58.010
He is good at engineering military weapons and drug production.

10:58.040 --> 10:59.770
He is evil

10:59.970 --> 11:02.390
but few has seen his face.

11:04.010 --> 11:05.900
Cold Spring

11:06.070 --> 11:08.710
is really unpredictable.

11:10.930 --> 11:13.290
Since Fu Ling saved you,

11:13.430 --> 11:14.590
you can take this chance

11:14.610 --> 11:15.570
to join Cold Spring

11:15.600 --> 11:16.720
to collect internal information

11:16.750 --> 11:18.080
to attack Zhen Yu's vital point

11:18.080 --> 11:19.320
and destroy his plan.

11:20.370 --> 11:21.580
Master, you...

11:22.310 --> 11:23.660
I know.

11:24.820 --> 11:26.910
This is putting you on the spot.

11:27.420 --> 11:29.180
But in the whole Eternals,

11:29.200 --> 11:30.080
you are the only immortal

11:30.110 --> 11:32.430
who can enter the Cold Spring.

11:32.500 --> 11:34.570
Since they want something from you,

11:34.700 --> 11:36.630
they won’t hurt you easily.

11:38.330 --> 11:39.310
Chong Zhao,

11:40.260 --> 11:42.950
I have always treated you as my own son.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.930
I don't want you

11:45.490 --> 11:48.490
to be in danger.

11:48.730 --> 11:49.630
But now,

11:49.630 --> 11:51.200
not only Lanling needs you,

11:51.200 --> 11:53.620
the all Eternals and demons need you.

11:53.650 --> 11:54.700
So I

11:54.720 --> 11:56.990
can only put you in danger.

11:57.010 --> 11:58.800
You have a strong moral mind.

11:58.920 --> 12:00.090
I believe

12:00.110 --> 12:01.880
even if you are withinin darkness,

12:02.090 --> 12:04.290
you won't be swallowed it.

12:12.500 --> 12:13.780
I understand.

12:16.750 --> 12:18.570
I will do my best

12:18.850 --> 12:20.000
and not let you down.

12:20.030 --> 12:21.550
I will investigate Cold Spring's schemes.

12:22.200 --> 12:23.080
Take care.

12:23.750 --> 12:26.280
All Eternals will be proud of you.

12:28.630 --> 12:29.650
Master.

12:30.790 --> 12:31.950
If Shuo asks–

12:32.000 --> 12:34.120
If you have to draw your sword against Bai Shuo,

12:34.120 --> 12:36.150
I will explain it to her.

12:38.190 --> 12:39.020
Okay.

12:50.430 --> 12:51.030
All right.

12:52.800 --> 12:53.490
Master.

12:53.520 --> 12:55.110
I think we should buy a five-person table.

12:55.130 --> 12:56.040
Why?

12:56.070 --> 12:57.810
I'm happy to sit with you.

12:57.940 --> 12:59.210
Do I look happy?

12:59.470 --> 13:01.080
I think you should be happy.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.320
Have a taste.

13:03.340 --> 13:04.100
These dishes

13:04.130 --> 13:05.930
were sincerely made by me.

13:05.950 --> 13:07.830
Even my aunt has never eaten my cooking.

13:07.850 --> 13:09.090
Here, try this.

13:10.450 --> 13:11.500
Here, Bai Shuo.

13:17.150 --> 13:18.020
It tastes good.

13:18.050 --> 13:18.890
Right?

13:24.330 --> 13:25.130
Bai Shuo.

13:25.450 --> 13:26.090
Why is

13:26.120 --> 13:27.320
your nose bleeding again?

13:30.720 --> 13:31.400
Again?

13:33.900 --> 13:34.900
What's going on?

13:35.800 --> 13:37.400
It bled a few times.

13:37.420 --> 13:38.930
Maybe it's because of internal heat.

13:39.060 --> 13:40.220
How many times?

13:40.660 --> 13:42.180
Two to three times?

13:42.210 --> 13:43.360
Three to four times?

13:43.800 --> 13:45.390
It's no big deal.

13:45.410 --> 13:46.850
You should not hide any of your

13:46.870 --> 13:48.080
health issues from me.

13:50.450 --> 13:51.450
When did this start?

13:51.950 --> 13:53.870
Since we returned from the Outlanders' City.

13:53.890 --> 13:55.610
Did this happen to the previous King of Outlanders

13:55.640 --> 13:56.670
after they put on the Outlander King's Ring?

13:56.720 --> 13:57.960
Not that I heard of.

14:00.210 --> 14:02.210
Does it have something to do with the ring?

14:03.310 --> 14:04.080
But...

14:04.300 --> 14:05.250
But what?

14:07.070 --> 14:09.950
When I put the sword back in the Outlanders' City's Underground Palace,

14:09.980 --> 14:11.440
I did feel a surge of

14:11.470 --> 14:12.970
new power in my body.

14:13.080 --> 14:14.480
Could it be that the Contemplation Stone reacted

14:14.480 --> 14:15.670
with the Divine Sword?

14:15.770 --> 14:17.480
Does this power still exist?

14:17.840 --> 14:18.960
I don't know.

14:18.990 --> 14:19.930
After that,

14:19.950 --> 14:21.340
feel that power anymore.

14:21.870 --> 14:23.150
Try activating your internal energy.

14:34.350 --> 14:35.010
Look.

14:35.040 --> 14:36.400
Nothing happened.

14:36.420 --> 14:38.440
Did the sword spirit mistake me for someone else?

14:39.390 --> 14:40.580
The Outlander King's Ring's doesn't acknowledge

14:40.640 --> 14:41.740
anyone as its owner easily.

14:45.050 --> 14:46.410
Lend me your turtle shell.

14:46.530 --> 14:47.980
Are you looking for my master again?

14:48.000 --> 14:50.120
If Lanling finds out, he'll be punished again.

14:50.150 --> 14:51.270
I'll be careful.

14:52.620 --> 14:53.500
I'll go too then.

14:53.530 --> 14:54.950
It's more convenient for me to go alone.

14:54.970 --> 14:56.210
You stay here

14:56.400 --> 14:57.430
to cultivate elixirs for me.

14:59.970 --> 15:01.050
Fine.

15:04.840 --> 15:06.780
Please say hello to Master for me.

15:06.940 --> 15:08.980
Don't put him on the spot.

15:22.490 --> 15:23.180
No.

15:24.570 --> 15:25.850
No one's eating

15:25.870 --> 15:27.110
such delicious food?

15:30.530 --> 15:32.460
My disciple's nose is bleeding?

15:32.490 --> 15:33.490
Why didn't she

15:33.510 --> 15:35.300
mention this in the letter?

15:36.030 --> 15:36.790
She said

15:36.790 --> 15:38.240
she has absorbed another Contemplation

15:38.240 --> 15:39.460
in the Outlanders' City.

15:39.490 --> 15:40.130
That's right.

15:44.690 --> 15:46.360
It's related to the Contemplation Stone.

15:46.380 --> 15:48.450
My disciple is a mortal.

15:48.470 --> 15:51.080
Yet the Contemplation Stone is an ancient divine object.

15:51.110 --> 15:52.990
Before a Contemplation is absorbed,

15:53.010 --> 15:55.010
Contemplation Stone is just a stone.

15:55.040 --> 15:56.710
The more it absorbs,

15:56.750 --> 15:58.630
the stronger the energy is.

15:58.650 --> 16:00.340
As a mortal,

16:00.370 --> 16:02.050
how can she handle

16:02.070 --> 16:03.280
divine power?

16:03.480 --> 16:05.120
The nose bleed

16:05.140 --> 16:06.880
is just the beginning.

16:06.900 --> 16:08.090
When the

16:08.120 --> 16:09.780
Five Contemplations are all gathered

16:09.810 --> 16:11.200
and the Contemplation Stone opens...

16:11.850 --> 16:13.090
What will happen?

16:15.510 --> 16:16.630
Her body explode and die.

16:18.060 --> 16:19.150
Why didn't you say that earlier?

16:19.150 --> 16:21.320
Although I know divination,

16:21.320 --> 16:22.840
I can only know after

16:22.840 --> 16:23.960
I calculate it.

16:23.960 --> 16:25.270
Only because you told me

16:25.270 --> 16:26.390
my disciple is sick,

16:26.390 --> 16:29.780
so I could tell it's because of the Contemplation Stone.

16:29.800 --> 16:30.960
How do we solve this?

16:32.340 --> 16:34.350
There is a way to do so.

16:34.370 --> 16:36.320
The Fox Clan has a treasure

16:36.350 --> 16:37.710
called Weak Water Stone.

16:37.750 --> 16:38.790
This is

16:38.790 --> 16:40.960
birthed from the love

16:40.960 --> 16:42.630
of the Fox Clan's ancestors.

16:42.630 --> 16:44.320
Whoever gets the Weak Water Stone

16:44.320 --> 16:46.500
will have endless spiritual power.

16:46.530 --> 16:48.370
This power can suppress

16:48.390 --> 16:51.100
Bai Shuo's backlash brought by the Contemplation Stone.

16:53.670 --> 16:55.670
My disciple said that you lost a star in Outlanders' City.

16:55.670 --> 16:56.820
Let me have a look.

16:56.850 --> 16:57.640
No need.

16:57.660 --> 16:58.710
I have things to tend to.

17:05.030 --> 17:06.990
You've been cultivating elixirs day and night.

17:07.020 --> 17:08.260
That's very sincere of you.

17:12.599 --> 17:13.750
What are you trying to say?

17:13.829 --> 17:15.000
Be straightforward.

17:15.400 --> 17:16.510
Since the first time Master

17:16.510 --> 17:18.030
brought you to Bright Moon Palace,

17:18.369 --> 17:20.130
I knew he now has a weakness.

17:21.109 --> 17:22.450
This weakness is you.

17:23.160 --> 17:24.550
The Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on him

17:24.569 --> 17:26.730
can only be erased by the divine power of the Contemplation Stone.

17:27.420 --> 17:29.770
I know he will never hurt you.

17:29.790 --> 17:30.750
If...

17:31.720 --> 17:33.630
If one day

17:34.270 --> 17:35.860
Master needs you,

17:36.570 --> 17:38.340
I hope you won't betray him.

17:40.890 --> 17:42.580
I will bind my life

17:42.610 --> 17:44.330
to Fan Yue's.

17:47.710 --> 17:49.200
Who wants

17:49.200 --> 17:50.250
that?

18:03.260 --> 18:04.530
What do you mean by that?

18:06.610 --> 18:08.410
What did you mean?

18:08.430 --> 18:09.820
Your life is yours.

18:09.850 --> 18:11.810
My life is mine.

18:11.840 --> 18:13.520
Why should they be bound?

18:16.540 --> 18:18.330
Did Master tell you something?

18:17.760 --> 18:24.310
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

18:18.360 --> 18:19.570
No.

18:20.310 --> 18:21.620
I'll ask him myself.

18:25.270 --> 18:31.270
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

18:31.030 --> 18:32.350
You weren't like this

18:32.350 --> 18:33.400
before you went to Master.

18:32.550 --> 18:35.370
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

18:33.420 --> 18:34.750
Like what?

18:34.780 --> 18:36.630
I've always been like this.

18:36.350 --> 18:39.830
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

18:40.610 --> 18:46.630
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

19:05.480 --> 19:06.760
You're not eating, drinking,

19:06.790 --> 19:08.120
nor making any noise.

19:08.640 --> 19:09.900
How calm of you.

19:10.120 --> 19:11.360
But

19:11.380 --> 19:12.830
I'm impatient.

19:13.670 --> 19:15.580
How about we play a game today?

19:15.610 --> 19:17.330
It's not fun if it's just the two of us playing it.

19:17.350 --> 19:18.390
We need more people.

19:18.780 --> 19:20.020
For example,

19:20.610 --> 19:22.890
with your Eternal friends.

19:25.330 --> 19:26.830
I don't understand what you mean.

19:26.860 --> 19:28.150
You're not killing me

19:28.180 --> 19:29.530
nor letting me go.

19:31.070 --> 19:32.830
What are you trying to do?

19:32.860 --> 19:34.540
I've never stopped you.

19:36.240 --> 19:37.330
But

19:37.350 --> 19:38.970
with your injury,

19:38.990 --> 19:40.790
can you walk out of Cold Spring?

19:41.290 --> 19:43.730
The other demons in Cold Spring Palace are different from me.

19:43.750 --> 19:46.310
If they catch a delicate Eternal,

19:46.340 --> 19:48.120
they will eat you.

19:49.620 --> 19:50.790
Divinity,

19:51.270 --> 19:53.280
the game I prepared for you

19:54.790 --> 19:56.820
is about to begin.

20:19.010 --> 20:20.490
What are you doing?

20:20.520 --> 20:21.820
I told you.

20:21.840 --> 20:23.560
I want to play a game

20:23.590 --> 20:24.900
with you.

20:32.250 --> 20:33.960
If you kill one of them,

20:33.990 --> 20:35.120
I'll let the rest

20:35.140 --> 20:36.470
go.

21:26.250 --> 21:27.400
Divinity.

21:27.590 --> 21:29.480
You wasted this opportunity.

21:36.510 --> 21:38.000
No!

21:37.730 --> 21:42.690
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

21:44.060 --> 21:45.370
If you listened to me,

21:45.400 --> 21:47.270
all four of them can live.

21:45.850 --> 21:51.480
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

21:47.290 --> 21:48.670
But you didn't give them

21:48.700 --> 21:50.450
the chance to live.

21:50.550 --> 21:52.570
I'll let you choose again.

21:52.780 --> 21:54.540
Kill one of these four.

21:54.140 --> 22:01.570
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

21:54.570 --> 21:55.920
As for the rest,

21:55.940 --> 21:57.270
I can let them go.

21:58.110 --> 21:59.200
You demoness...

21:59.620 --> 22:02.070
Why don't you just kill me?

22:02.100 --> 22:04.540
It's boring to kill you.

22:02.490 --> 22:07.540
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

22:04.560 --> 22:06.610
It's fun to force you to kill an Eternal.

22:06.640 --> 22:07.710
Why?

22:08.340 --> 22:09.670
You can't do it?

22:15.220 --> 22:18.670
♫Across thousands of miles♫

22:17.220 --> 22:18.290
Fellow Eternal...

22:18.740 --> 22:19.940
Fellow Eternal...

22:21.130 --> 22:22.380
Fellow Eternal...

22:22.470 --> 22:23.790
Divinity Chong Zhao,

22:23.310 --> 22:28.160
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

22:23.820 --> 22:26.610
you lost another chance to save your fellow Eternal.

22:26.630 --> 22:28.230
Now there are three people left.

22:28.260 --> 22:29.630
The rules are the same.

22:29.650 --> 22:30.850
Let's start.

22:30.950 --> 22:38.160
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

22:39.230 --> 22:44.020
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

22:46.760 --> 22:52.370
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

22:54.990 --> 23:00.500
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

23:03.450 --> 23:10.290
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

23:10.940 --> 23:15.480
♫I'm your wanderer♫

23:14.350 --> 23:15.480
Sorry...

23:19.030 --> 23:23.310
♫The flowers flew away♫

23:27.200 --> 23:31.050
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

23:34.920 --> 23:42.290
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

23:42.910 --> 23:48.630
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

23:42.960 --> 23:44.110
Go

23:55.490 --> 23:57.120
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

23:57.430 --> 23:59.400
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

23:59.650 --> 24:01.350
♫My love brought tears♫

24:01.550 --> 24:03.350
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

24:02.560 --> 24:04.390
Didn't you say you'd let them go?

24:03.790 --> 24:05.410
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

24:05.830 --> 24:07.180
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

24:06.090 --> 24:07.240
This is the second thing

24:07.240 --> 24:08.920
about being demon I'm teaching you.

24:07.370 --> 24:08.800
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

24:09.170 --> 24:09.860
A demon

24:09.450 --> 24:10.740
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

24:09.890 --> 24:11.440
is not credible.

24:11.560 --> 24:13.030
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

24:13.360 --> 24:15.280
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

24:13.840 --> 24:16.640
The evil insects Chen Ye made are really something.

24:15.510 --> 24:17.590
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

24:16.660 --> 24:18.270
I'm really looking forward to how amazing

24:17.940 --> 24:19.430
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

24:18.300 --> 24:19.610
he will be after he has absorbed

24:19.630 --> 24:20.630
enough demon pith, Eternal arteries,

24:19.850 --> 24:21.570
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

24:20.660 --> 24:22.590
and human lives.

24:21.860 --> 24:23.800
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

24:24.010 --> 24:25.570
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

24:25.930 --> 24:28.190
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

24:27.630 --> 24:28.880
Other than Fu Ling,

24:28.880 --> 24:30.110
there's another Demon Lord

24:30.540 --> 24:33.390
named Chen Ye under Zhen Yu.

24:33.650 --> 24:35.930
He is good at engineering military weapons and drug production.

24:36.290 --> 24:37.890
He is evil

24:37.960 --> 24:40.600
but few has seen his face.

24:44.070 --> 24:45.070
I've killed an Eternal

24:45.070 --> 24:46.340
and betrayed my sect

24:47.480 --> 24:48.790
as you wished.

24:49.210 --> 24:50.720
Are you satisfied?

24:51.520 --> 24:52.800
Welcome, Lord Chong Zhao,

24:52.820 --> 24:54.820
to the Cold Spring Palace.

25:09.320 --> 25:10.120
Master.

25:11.810 --> 25:13.180
What happened?

25:13.200 --> 25:14.950
-What’s wrong–
-Bai Shuo can't absorb Contemplations anymore.

25:15.210 --> 25:16.570
Why?

25:17.080 --> 25:18.850
She's just a human.

25:19.020 --> 25:20.980
She can't withstand the divine power of the Contemplation Stone.

25:21.290 --> 25:22.960
The nosebleed is just the beginning.

25:23.620 --> 25:25.230
If she keeps absorbing Contemplations,

25:26.600 --> 25:28.460
her body will explode.

25:28.480 --> 25:29.960
What about you?

25:30.040 --> 25:32.040
Are you going to give up collecting Contemplations for her?

25:33.060 --> 25:34.200
I thought you and her

25:34.200 --> 25:36.000
have established some friendship.

25:37.650 --> 25:38.850
Bai Shuo saved the Outlanders' City

25:38.880 --> 25:39.840
and Hua Yong,

25:39.870 --> 25:41.630
I can repay that with my life.

25:41.650 --> 25:43.770
But this concerns your life.

25:43.930 --> 25:45.890
Bright Moon Palace needs its master.

25:46.930 --> 25:48.500
The world goes on even if

25:48.530 --> 25:50.030
someone is not here anymore.

25:51.330 --> 25:53.680
My life is up to me.

25:55.000 --> 25:56.640
Even the heavens can't stop me

25:57.320 --> 25:58.890
from protecting the people I want to.

26:01.560 --> 26:02.560
Where is Mu Jiu?

26:03.000 --> 26:04.180
He's still in the Unbridled Pavilion, right?

26:04.290 --> 26:05.370
Mu Jiu?

26:05.890 --> 26:08.260
There is a treasure called Weak Water Stone in the Fox Clan.

26:08.780 --> 26:10.540
If Bai Shuo can have that,

26:10.770 --> 26:12.630
she can suppress Contemplation Stone's backlash.

26:13.740 --> 26:15.370
I'll go look for Mu Jiu now.

26:28.090 --> 26:29.160
Huo?

26:30.200 --> 26:31.290
Why are you here?

26:33.450 --> 26:34.970
Why are you in my room

26:35.000 --> 26:36.450
in the middle of the night?

26:36.950 --> 26:37.880
You miss me?

26:38.880 --> 26:40.400
I heard that there are many treasures

26:40.480 --> 26:41.720
in Jingyou Mountain.

26:42.880 --> 26:43.810
Why are you

26:43.840 --> 26:45.630
coveting the treasure of our Fox Clan?

26:46.080 --> 26:47.160
But it doesn't matter.

26:47.180 --> 26:48.230
You're Huo.

26:48.260 --> 26:49.050
I can give you

26:49.080 --> 26:50.550
any treasure you want.

26:50.840 --> 26:51.910
But...

26:51.930 --> 26:53.170
But what?

26:53.700 --> 26:55.830
Today's been tiring.

26:55.860 --> 26:56.690
I have a headache

26:56.710 --> 26:57.950
and I feel uncomfortable.

26:57.980 --> 26:59.150
If someone

26:59.170 --> 27:00.510
can give me a massage,

27:00.540 --> 27:01.850
maybe...

27:05.690 --> 27:07.190
I was just kidding.

27:07.380 --> 27:08.450
Just kidding.

27:08.480 --> 27:10.480
You don't have to...

27:15.170 --> 27:16.240
Massage where?

27:19.680 --> 27:20.570
Then...

27:20.600 --> 27:21.560
Massage here.

27:23.490 --> 27:24.270
It hurts.

27:24.290 --> 27:25.250
It hurts...

27:25.270 --> 27:27.350
Here, here...

27:29.250 --> 27:29.870
It hurts!

27:29.890 --> 27:30.770
It hurts.

27:34.160 --> 27:35.200
That's enough.

27:35.500 --> 27:36.480
It's great.

27:39.350 --> 27:40.350
By the way,

27:40.370 --> 27:41.370
our Fox Clan has

27:41.400 --> 27:42.440
many treasures.

27:42.460 --> 27:43.330
Which one do you want?

27:43.890 --> 27:44.770
How about this?

27:44.790 --> 27:45.660
Why don't you

27:45.690 --> 27:47.050
go back to Jingyou Mountain with me

27:47.070 --> 27:48.870
and be my wife?

27:48.900 --> 27:49.550
By then,

27:49.570 --> 27:50.640
you can choose whatever treasure

27:50.670 --> 27:51.760
you want.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.240
Young Master.

27:56.920 --> 27:57.480
Young Master.

27:57.510 --> 27:58.800
You're really here.

27:59.010 --> 28:00.210
Chang Sheng?

28:01.450 --> 28:02.260
Elder,

28:02.290 --> 28:03.290
why are you here?

28:03.310 --> 28:04.070
Master has ordered

28:03.390 --> 28:05.120
[Chang Sheng,
Demon Race,
Elder of Fox Clan]

28:04.070 --> 28:05.510
for me to take you back to Jingyou Mountain.

28:05.910 --> 28:06.920
I'm not going back.

28:06.950 --> 28:08.130
Master said

28:08.160 --> 28:09.290
if you don't obey,

28:09.310 --> 28:10.910
I can use force.

28:11.800 --> 28:12.870
Huo, save me.

28:13.640 --> 28:15.180
Since your master has given the order,

28:15.200 --> 28:16.960
if I were to stop you,

28:16.990 --> 28:18.270
it would be rude of me.

28:18.290 --> 28:19.340
But our master asked me

28:19.370 --> 28:20.750
to protect your young master.

28:20.980 --> 28:22.730
If I lose him,

28:22.830 --> 28:24.070
I won't be able to explain it.

28:24.490 --> 28:25.530
What do you want then?

28:25.550 --> 28:27.550
Your young master invited me to the Fox Clan.

28:27.860 --> 28:29.530
Let me be your guest then.

28:31.570 --> 28:33.400
But that's not an invitation from my master.

28:33.420 --> 28:35.030
But I want to go.

28:41.170 --> 28:41.900
Shuo.

28:43.070 --> 28:43.870
Are you okay?

28:52.340 --> 28:53.670
The human body

28:53.710 --> 28:55.940
can't withstand the power of the Contemplation Stone.

28:55.970 --> 28:57.650
If this continues,

28:57.670 --> 28:59.950
Bai Shuo will die.

29:00.250 --> 29:01.210
Fan Yue,

29:01.240 --> 29:03.380
if you really care about her,

29:03.490 --> 29:04.630
you can't allow her

29:04.680 --> 29:06.550
to continue absorbing the Five Contemplations.

29:10.170 --> 29:11.130
Go back and rest.

29:11.390 --> 29:12.840
I don't need you to cultivate elixirs anymore.

29:14.240 --> 29:15.620
You said yesterday that

29:16.090 --> 29:17.570
your life is yours

29:17.590 --> 29:19.110
and my life is mine.

29:19.220 --> 29:21.110
Please behave yourself.

29:21.130 --> 29:22.640
Leave me alone.

29:27.600 --> 29:28.250
Master.

29:28.280 --> 29:29.120
Bad news.

29:29.140 --> 29:30.760
Something happened to Tian Huo and Mu Jiu.

29:34.070 --> 29:35.800
I've searched all of Unbridled Pavilion.

29:35.830 --> 29:37.460
It's neat everywhere else.

29:37.480 --> 29:39.240
Only Mu Jiu's room has signs of fighting.

29:39.270 --> 29:40.360
Tian Huo and Mu Jiu

29:40.380 --> 29:41.950
must have disappeared here.

29:46.820 --> 29:48.060
It's the Fox Clan.

29:48.830 --> 29:51.240
Did Tian Huo go to the Fox Clan to look for the Weak Water Stone?

29:51.610 --> 29:53.790
This is a burn mark left by a Fox Clan spell.

29:55.410 --> 29:56.620
A Fox Clan spell?

29:57.030 --> 29:57.750
Master.

29:57.830 --> 29:58.960
Bright Moon Palace and Fox Clan

29:58.960 --> 30:00.440
never interfere with each other.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.640
It must be Mu Jiu who caused the trouble.

30:01.640 --> 30:02.830
He was kidnapped along with the Tian Huo.

30:02.830 --> 30:03.350
Master.

30:03.350 --> 30:04.960
Let's go to the Fox Clan to save them.

30:08.920 --> 30:09.720
Your Highness,

30:09.720 --> 30:11.480
Ms. Bai, why aren't you worried?

30:11.510 --> 30:13.140
Tian Huo knows what to do.

30:13.160 --> 30:14.200
Her spiritual power is not weak either.

30:14.230 --> 30:15.920
Even if Fox Clan's Chang Mei came,

30:15.940 --> 30:17.490
they couldn't have taken the both of them away

30:17.520 --> 30:19.800
from Unbridled Pavilion without making a sound.

30:19.830 --> 30:20.940
What do you mean?

30:20.960 --> 30:22.850
It's easy for Tian Huo

30:22.880 --> 30:24.400
to make some noise.

30:25.420 --> 30:26.450
Obviously,

30:26.500 --> 30:28.080
she didn't want to alarm us.

30:28.610 --> 30:29.440
Why?

30:29.620 --> 30:30.980
If they alarmed you,

30:31.010 --> 30:32.370
they wouldn't be able to leave.

30:32.690 --> 30:33.370
Then,

30:33.400 --> 30:35.230
Tian Huo couldn't go to the Fox Clan.

30:35.700 --> 30:36.920
You mean

30:37.000 --> 30:38.370
Tian Huo wasn't abducted?

30:38.400 --> 30:40.210
She went to the Fox Clan willingly?

30:45.990 --> 30:48.710
[Jingyou Mountain,
Demon Race]

31:02.770 --> 31:03.730
Aunt!

31:06.270 --> 31:08.600
If I hadn't sent Chang Sheng to find you,

31:08.230 --> 31:10.980
[Chang Mei,
Demon Race,
Master of Jingyou Mountain]

31:09.520 --> 31:11.290
will you still remember me?

31:12.930 --> 31:14.440
Greetings, Master of Jingyou Mountain.

31:20.290 --> 31:22.330
No need for the formalities, Lady Tian Huo.

31:22.600 --> 31:23.550
I don’t deserve being greeted

31:23.550 --> 31:25.330
by the guardian of the Bright Moon Palace.

31:25.360 --> 31:27.970
You are one of the Three Kings of the Demon Race.

31:27.990 --> 31:29.870
How could you say that?

31:29.900 --> 31:30.890
Is that so?

31:31.290 --> 31:33.130
Then why did you

31:33.160 --> 31:34.800
come uninvited?

31:36.100 --> 31:36.820
Aunt.

31:36.850 --> 31:38.440
This has nothing to do with Tian Huo.

31:38.770 --> 31:39.730
I know.

31:39.750 --> 31:41.340
You want me to come back to Jingyou Mountain

31:41.370 --> 31:42.760
to force me to inherit the Master position

31:42.790 --> 31:43.870
and manage Jingyou Mountain, right?

31:43.990 --> 31:45.230
Aunt,

31:45.410 --> 31:47.580
don't you know what I'm capable of?

31:47.610 --> 31:48.440
Me?

31:48.460 --> 31:49.410
Manage the Fox Clan?

31:49.840 --> 31:50.830
I'm not worthy.

31:50.880 --> 31:53.110
What do you want to do if not that then?

31:54.570 --> 31:55.860
Join the Bright Moon Palace?

31:56.120 --> 31:57.030
Three days later will be

31:57.030 --> 31:58.880
the ceremony of you becoming the Master.

31:58.980 --> 32:00.270
Chang Sheng and Chang Wu have made the preperations

32:00.270 --> 32:01.270
for the ceremony.

32:01.680 --> 32:03.170
You're not allowed to go anywhere these few days.

32:03.380 --> 32:04.790
Otherwise, I'll break your leg.

32:04.810 --> 32:06.330
Why do you want me to inherit your position?

32:06.360 --> 32:07.710
I said I don't want to.

32:07.730 --> 32:08.870
You don't want to?

32:08.900 --> 32:09.710
Fine.

32:09.730 --> 32:11.660
I shall kill

32:12.010 --> 32:13.600
Lady Tian Huo then.

32:19.870 --> 32:20.890
Cang Shan.

32:21.080 --> 32:22.140
Get ready.

32:22.330 --> 32:24.240
We'll set off to Jingyou Mountain now.

32:30.130 --> 32:30.970
You stay.

32:31.780 --> 32:32.820
Why?

32:33.350 --> 32:34.640
This is a Bright Moon Palace matter.

32:34.640 --> 32:35.980
It has nothing to do with you.

32:36.010 --> 32:37.250
Tian Huo and I went through

32:37.270 --> 32:38.560
thick and thin in Outlanders' City.

32:38.600 --> 32:39.870
We're friends.

32:39.910 --> 32:40.990
There must be a reason

32:41.010 --> 32:42.340
for her going to the Fox Clan.

32:42.370 --> 32:43.170
As her friend, I should–

32:43.190 --> 32:44.780
Where she goes has nothing to do with you.

32:45.600 --> 32:47.080
Jingyou Mountain is a demon territory.

32:47.100 --> 32:47.920
You're a human

32:47.920 --> 32:48.790
with no spiritual power.

32:48.810 --> 32:49.570
If you follow us,

32:49.600 --> 32:50.710
you'll only drag us down.

33:00.850 --> 33:02.890
How can you threaten me with Tian Huo?

33:03.090 --> 33:04.490
This has nothing to do with her.

33:04.510 --> 33:06.620
Why didn't you come home?

33:06.650 --> 33:07.970
You first went to the Outlanders' City,

33:08.000 --> 33:09.390
then you went to the Human Race.

33:09.420 --> 33:10.330
How many days has it been?

33:10.360 --> 33:11.830
I haven't heard from you at all.

33:12.270 --> 33:13.680
Do you really care about the Fox Clan

33:13.700 --> 33:15.090
or me at all?

33:16.050 --> 33:17.000
These...

33:17.660 --> 33:19.340
These are all my fault.

33:19.370 --> 33:21.220
But Tian Huo has nothing to do with these.

33:21.660 --> 33:22.790
I insisted on following her.

33:22.810 --> 33:23.610
Shut up!

33:25.180 --> 33:26.570
She's under Fan Yue.

33:27.330 --> 33:28.490
Don’t you know the relationship

33:28.510 --> 33:30.780
between Jingyou Mountain and Bright Moon Palace?

33:30.880 --> 33:33.170
Why would she approach you of all people?

33:33.300 --> 33:35.270
What is she up to?

33:35.600 --> 33:37.420
Have you ever thought about it with your brain?

33:37.640 --> 33:39.510
Master, that's not right.

33:39.790 --> 33:41.360
Jingyou Mountain and Bright Moon Palace

33:41.390 --> 33:42.860
never interfered with each other.

33:42.880 --> 33:44.760
You are the leader of the clan.

33:45.270 --> 33:46.240
You should think

33:46.240 --> 33:47.790
before you speak.

33:48.400 --> 33:49.310
How dare you

33:50.800 --> 33:52.040
refute me?

33:52.060 --> 33:52.860
I dare not.

33:53.290 --> 33:54.730
But this concerns my master.

33:55.120 --> 33:56.800
I must explain.

34:22.989 --> 34:24.070
Master?

34:24.090 --> 34:25.130
Why are you here?

34:25.159 --> 34:28.219
Did the tortoise shell I gave you break?

34:28.350 --> 34:30.380
I sensed the tortoise shell cracking,

34:30.409 --> 34:31.639
so I came to see it.

34:31.920 --> 34:32.989
Where is Fan Yue?

34:35.560 --> 34:36.480
You fought?

34:37.360 --> 34:38.400
Master.

34:38.420 --> 34:40.670
What did Fan Yue talk to you about?

34:40.699 --> 34:41.670
After he came back,

34:41.670 --> 34:43.030
it was like he's a different person.

34:43.030 --> 34:44.889
The two of you...

34:44.909 --> 34:46.110
one's terribly unlucky

34:46.110 --> 34:46.800
and the other is living hell.

34:46.800 --> 34:47.840
You two can make a scene

34:47.840 --> 34:48.590
behind closed doors.

34:48.590 --> 34:51.150
But why do you have to torture me too?

34:52.400 --> 34:53.150
Fine.

34:53.150 --> 34:55.860
I've lived thousands of years.

34:55.880 --> 34:57.680
I shall consider doing this for merit.

34:57.710 --> 34:58.910
Let me ask you.

34:58.930 --> 35:00.410
Did Fan Yue

35:00.440 --> 35:01.750
go somewhere far?

35:01.770 --> 35:02.920
How did you know?

35:03.210 --> 35:04.290
Not only do I know,

35:04.310 --> 35:06.930
I also know that he went to the Fox Clan.

35:07.140 --> 35:08.540
You know that too?

35:08.880 --> 35:10.720
Why didn't he take you there?

35:10.740 --> 35:11.930
He said I'm an outsider.

35:11.960 --> 35:13.560
If I don't have spiritual power, I'll only drag them down.

35:13.580 --> 35:14.540
So they didn't let me follow me.

35:14.590 --> 35:16.760
Why can't you use your tricks

35:16.760 --> 35:19.590
when it comes to him?

35:19.590 --> 35:21.380
You believe whatever he says?

35:21.400 --> 35:22.790
Of course not.

35:23.050 --> 35:25.570
I just don't want to fight him head-on again.

35:25.700 --> 35:26.710
If you didn't come,

35:26.710 --> 35:28.890
I was going to ask the Fox Clan.

35:28.910 --> 35:29.840
Master,

35:29.870 --> 35:31.150
be straightforward.

35:31.170 --> 35:32.040
Don't hide things from me.

35:32.070 --> 35:33.030
And don't lie to me.

35:33.050 --> 35:34.830
I can tell you.

35:34.860 --> 35:35.630
But

35:35.630 --> 35:37.850
you have to answer a question first.

35:37.870 --> 35:39.280
What is it?

35:39.310 --> 35:41.430
Do you have feelings for Fan Yue?

35:58.390 --> 35:59.030
How...

35:59.050 --> 36:00.450
How is that possible?

36:00.480 --> 36:02.730
I'm mad at him now.

36:02.750 --> 36:03.940
How could he

36:03.970 --> 36:05.510
just change like that?

36:06.070 --> 36:06.950
Look.

36:06.970 --> 36:08.900
You're so in love.

36:08.930 --> 36:10.890
In the letter you wrote to me,

36:10.920 --> 36:12.390
it was all about Fan Yue.

36:12.410 --> 36:14.080
Your mood changes

36:14.110 --> 36:16.150
with his mood.

36:16.150 --> 36:18.150
How can you say you're not in love?

36:18.890 --> 36:19.810
I...

36:21.830 --> 36:24.390
The lovers in this world

36:24.420 --> 36:25.940
do all things

36:25.960 --> 36:26.730
for each other,

36:26.760 --> 36:28.430
yet they always misunderstand

36:28.450 --> 36:30.220
and even miss out each other.

36:31.610 --> 36:32.530
My disciple,

36:32.560 --> 36:34.890
there are only two stars left on Fan Yue.

36:34.920 --> 36:37.430
But now he's going to the Fox Clan for a treasure.

36:37.590 --> 36:38.830
It's dangerous.

36:38.860 --> 36:39.740
A treasure?

36:39.760 --> 36:40.990
Fan Yue went

36:41.020 --> 36:43.580
for a treasure of the Fox Clan

36:43.600 --> 36:44.690
called Weak Water Stone.

36:44.720 --> 36:46.510
But the master of the Fox Clan  Chang Mei

36:46.550 --> 36:47.920
has a bad temper and is inflexible.

36:47.920 --> 36:50.510
How could she give away the treasure so easily?

36:50.870 --> 36:53.470
You know how badly Fan Yue is injured.

36:53.540 --> 36:55.770
There will be a fierce battle.

36:55.790 --> 36:57.100
Why did he go to get a treasure?

36:57.120 --> 36:58.510
Does that need a reason?

36:58.510 --> 37:00.400
Of course it's because...

37:01.400 --> 37:03.540
this treasure is good.

37:03.850 --> 37:05.730
With Fan Yue's current condition,

37:05.750 --> 37:07.780
if he fights with the entire Fox Clan,

37:07.800 --> 37:08.770
another star

37:08.790 --> 37:10.460
might fall.

37:14.710 --> 37:15.360
My good disciple!

37:15.360 --> 37:16.710
Don't tell Fan Yue I told you this

37:16.710 --> 37:18.280
when you see him!

37:21.000 --> 37:22.000
Aunt,

37:22.030 --> 37:23.550
I lost my parents when I was young.

37:23.570 --> 37:25.420
You raised me.

37:25.480 --> 37:26.440
In my heart,

37:26.440 --> 37:28.150
I've treated you as my own mother.

37:28.210 --> 37:29.630
Even if I marry Tian Huo,

37:29.630 --> 37:32.150
I will never forget you.

37:35.580 --> 37:37.490
I was born weaker than others.

37:38.050 --> 37:39.580
When I was young,

37:39.610 --> 37:41.000
there weren't many I could defeat.

37:41.530 --> 37:43.220
I was bullied for this.

37:44.000 --> 37:45.200
I've grown up now.

37:45.220 --> 37:46.300
Those guys

37:46.330 --> 37:47.920
seem to respect me and fear me,

37:47.940 --> 37:49.870
but it's all for your sake.

37:50.380 --> 37:51.870
It's fine if it was in the past.

37:51.890 --> 37:54.040
I fear nothing in this vast world cause I'm reckless.

37:54.100 --> 37:55.180
But this time,

37:55.440 --> 37:57.400
after being to the Outlanders' City,

37:57.540 --> 37:59.380
I found out the world is so huge

37:59.410 --> 38:01.040
and there are countless powerful Eternals and demons.

38:01.120 --> 38:01.990
Aunt,

38:02.010 --> 38:03.410
if you really hand over

38:03.440 --> 38:04.730
the Fox Clan to me,

38:04.750 --> 38:05.630
aren't you afraid

38:05.660 --> 38:07.130
I will ruin the foundation

38:07.150 --> 38:08.050
you've build up over thousands of years?

38:08.900 --> 38:10.500
Since you know these,

38:10.520 --> 38:12.150
you should practice harder

38:12.360 --> 38:13.790
so that you can protect yourself

38:13.810 --> 38:14.860
and the Fox Clan,

38:14.960 --> 38:16.740
instead of chasing after women

38:16.760 --> 38:17.750
without proper behavior.

38:18.710 --> 38:19.790
Aunt,

38:20.040 --> 38:21.760
I know how you feel.

38:23.020 --> 38:24.270
But I don't want to

38:24.320 --> 38:25.970
go against my will.

38:26.160 --> 38:27.440
I like Tian Huo.

38:27.560 --> 38:29.370
I like freedom.

38:30.410 --> 38:32.050
Jingyou Mountain is too small.

38:32.680 --> 38:34.640
The responsibility of a master is too much too.

38:35.810 --> 38:36.730
Aunt,

38:36.750 --> 38:38.180
if you really care about me,

38:38.340 --> 38:39.820
please let me go.

38:40.930 --> 38:43.020
I also want to make you happy.

38:43.130 --> 38:43.990
But...

38:46.830 --> 38:48.130
You're willing to

38:48.820 --> 38:50.940
give up everything for Tian Huo.

38:50.970 --> 38:51.970
But what about her?

38:52.160 --> 38:53.430
Does she like you?

38:53.450 --> 38:55.010
She...

38:55.760 --> 38:57.630
She doesn't like me now.

38:57.650 --> 38:58.930
That's because we're not close enough.

38:59.080 --> 38:59.960
When she gets to know me,

38:59.990 --> 39:00.470
she will definitely–

39:00.490 --> 39:02.130
You opened those pistachios

39:02.160 --> 39:03.640
for her, right?

39:04.270 --> 39:05.940
You're a young master after all.

39:05.970 --> 39:07.250
Since when did you do such things?

39:08.590 --> 39:09.840
Even a blind can tell

39:09.840 --> 39:11.300
you like her.

39:11.330 --> 39:12.130
Jiu,

39:12.420 --> 39:14.110
you're just deceiving yourself.

39:14.640 --> 39:16.720
I can't persuade you for things like love.

39:17.740 --> 39:19.620
But you have to promise me

39:20.550 --> 39:21.810
to inherit the position of the master.

39:23.170 --> 39:24.370
But not now.

39:25.210 --> 39:26.400
What do you mean?

39:26.430 --> 39:27.440
Three days.

39:27.480 --> 39:29.210
I'll give you three days.

39:29.230 --> 39:31.390
If you can make Tian Huo fall in love with you,

39:31.530 --> 39:33.380
then be prepared to welcome

39:33.880 --> 39:36.810
the grandest wedding of the Fox Clan for you.

39:37.440 --> 39:40.080
But if Tian Huo doesn't like you

39:40.100 --> 39:42.320
no matter how hard you try,

39:42.820 --> 39:44.170
that means it's not worthy for you

39:44.200 --> 39:46.000
to give up on everything for her.

39:46.670 --> 39:48.100
So you must then

39:48.600 --> 39:49.810
inherit this position.

39:51.020 --> 39:51.950
What do you think?

39:52.260 --> 39:53.500
Do you dare?

40:03.770 --> 40:04.570
Master.

40:04.600 --> 40:05.990
You’ve always brought Bai Shuo along with you.

40:06.010 --> 40:07.290
Why did you suddenly stop doing so?

40:07.310 --> 40:08.790
Also,

40:08.840 --> 40:09.930
you've been a little

40:09.960 --> 40:11.330
fierce to Bai Shuo these few days.

40:21.400 --> 40:22.170
Master.

40:22.200 --> 40:23.260
How are you going in?

40:23.290 --> 40:24.290
In a civilized manner

40:24.360 --> 40:25.560
or with brute force?

40:25.590 --> 40:26.800
Let’s split up.

40:27.670 --> 40:30.070
I need you to do something else.

40:31.870 --> 40:32.640
Master.

40:33.250 --> 40:34.280
The succession concerns the

40:34.280 --> 40:36.030
rise and fall of the Fox Clan.

40:36.050 --> 40:37.610
After all, Mu Jiu is still young.

40:37.640 --> 40:39.790
He doesn't have many achievements in the clan.

40:39.960 --> 40:41.400
If you pass the position so rashly,

40:40.520 --> 40:42.070
[Chang Wu, Demon Race, Elder of the Fox Clan]
[Chang Sheng, Demon Race, Elder of the Fox Clan]

40:41.420 --> 40:42.220
wouldn't it be...

40:44.160 --> 40:45.430
This position

40:45.450 --> 40:47.820
is passed down within the family.

40:47.850 --> 40:49.960
I have the final say of who it goes to.

40:49.980 --> 40:51.590
You can be it if you want.

40:51.650 --> 40:53.250
How about you go solve

40:53.280 --> 40:54.550
the problem with the Love Tree?

40:54.570 --> 40:55.740
That's not what I meant.

40:55.770 --> 40:56.600
But...

40:56.620 --> 40:58.060
We don't need to discuss this anymore.

40:58.700 --> 41:00.450
As for Jiu,

41:00.480 --> 41:02.370
Tian Huo clearly doesn't love him.

41:02.610 --> 41:05.300
As long as Tian Huo can stay in the Fox Clan for three days,

41:05.800 --> 41:08.240
the succession of the throne will happen naturally.

41:09.090 --> 41:09.880
Chang Wu.

41:09.900 --> 41:10.830
Keep an eye on them.

41:10.860 --> 41:12.140
Report to me

41:12.160 --> 41:13.370
if they have any movements.

41:13.400 --> 41:14.290
Yes.

41:15.630 --> 41:16.620
But Master,

41:17.250 --> 41:18.560
the person behind Tian Huo

41:18.580 --> 41:19.790
is not to be trifled with.

41:19.820 --> 41:21.360
We broke into the Unbridled Pavilion.

41:21.670 --> 41:23.220
If we detain her now,

41:23.440 --> 41:24.330
I'm afraid...

41:24.770 --> 41:25.610
What are you afraid of?

41:26.460 --> 41:27.790
Even if the sky falls,

41:27.810 --> 41:28.920
you'd push me

41:28.920 --> 41:30.150
to take the responsibility.

41:30.720 --> 41:33.200
All these years, the affairs of the Fox Clan have always been like this.

41:33.220 --> 41:35.090
Now you're being loyal?

41:37.680 --> 41:38.610
Master.

41:38.650 --> 41:40.000
Master of Bright Moon is here.

41:59.890 --> 42:01.180
Master of Bright Moon is here.

42:01.210 --> 42:01.810
We’re doomed.

42:01.830 --> 42:03.540
Are we going to be wiped out?

42:03.570 --> 42:04.860
He's up to no good, right?

42:06.880 --> 42:08.360
Our master is powerfull too.

42:08.380 --> 42:09.320
Let's go and have a look.

42:09.320 --> 42:09.850
Okay.

42:24.630 --> 42:26.590
All irrelevant people, leave.

42:26.800 --> 42:27.960
I have something

42:27.960 --> 42:29.480
to talk to Master Fan about.

42:30.550 --> 42:31.480
Let's go.

42:37.630 --> 42:38.720
Master Fan,

42:38.820 --> 42:41.070
are you here for Tian Huo?

42:41.610 --> 42:43.200
I'll be frank with you.

42:43.280 --> 42:45.070
Lady Tian Huo is indeed in my mountain.

42:45.110 --> 42:45.980
But

42:46.220 --> 42:48.270
I can’t give her back to you today.

42:48.300 --> 42:49.380
Why?

42:49.400 --> 42:51.610
You must know that there's something going on

42:51.730 --> 42:53.400
between Mu Jiu and Tian Huo.

42:53.430 --> 42:55.520
My nephew is a romantic guy.

42:55.930 --> 42:57.180
I promised him

42:57.210 --> 42:58.600
to give him three days

42:58.620 --> 43:00.180
to win the heart of Tian Huo.

43:00.900 --> 43:02.190
If possible,

43:02.220 --> 43:04.180
we will hold a wedding for them.

43:04.200 --> 43:05.160
Wedding?

43:05.760 --> 43:07.550
You Fox Clan like to do things

43:07.550 --> 43:08.880
on your own accord.

43:10.540 --> 43:12.230
From the Outlanders' City's chaos,

43:12.450 --> 43:14.610
you should've guess that

43:14.880 --> 43:16.610
the Cold Spring Palace's snake

43:16.640 --> 43:18.410
is plotting something terrible.

43:18.520 --> 43:20.610
Even if you have great demon power,

43:20.630 --> 43:22.650
it's better to have Jingyou Mountain as your friend

43:22.870 --> 43:25.350
than having another enemy

43:25.380 --> 43:26.780
while surrounded by other enemies, right?

43:27.900 --> 43:29.580
Are you threatening me?

43:31.100 --> 43:31.830
No.

43:32.690 --> 43:34.400
I'm asking for your help.

43:35.150 --> 43:37.060
My nephew is born with weak demonic power.

43:37.090 --> 43:39.550
But demons always revere the strong.

43:39.860 --> 43:41.020
I fear that

43:41.250 --> 43:42.210
when I'm gone,

43:42.280 --> 43:43.670
he will have no one to rely on.

43:43.970 --> 43:45.710
Since Mu Jiu likes Tian Huo,

43:45.830 --> 43:47.650
if they can get married,

43:48.130 --> 43:49.920
with the support of the Bright Moon Palace,

43:49.950 --> 43:51.390
I can rest assured.

43:52.050 --> 43:53.490
Consider it as me

43:53.520 --> 43:55.330
owing you a favor.

43:56.050 --> 43:57.490
No need.

43:58.630 --> 44:00.400
Tian Huo can decide her personal matters.

44:00.710 --> 44:02.880
If you want me to protect Mu Jiu,

44:03.040 --> 44:04.330
that's not a problem too.

44:05.030 --> 44:06.920
But I want something.

44:07.360 --> 44:08.360
What is it?

44:09.360 --> 44:10.690
The Weak Water Stone.
